const LineRedHorr = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <svg>
        <line
          x1="0"
          y1="0"
          x2="800"
          y2="0"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke="#7e0000"
          width="800"
        />
      </svg>
    </>
  )
}

export default LineRedHorr
